OL,3,C'A community win': Plans for water
OL,4,Cpark resort in derelict quarry blocked
OL,6,FPlans for a controversial water park
OL,7,Fresort on the site of a derelict
OL,8,Fquarry in a Derbyshire village, have
OL,9,Fbeen refused at a council meeting.
OL,11,FHundreds of residents were opposed to
OL,12,Fthe development called "Amber Rock".
OL,14,FPlans were announced in 2019 with
OL,15,Fdesigns submitted two years ago, but
OL,16,Ftoday marked an end to the fight from
OL,17,Fthose against the plans in and around
OL,18,FCrich.
OL,20,FIf approved, the development would
OL,21,Fhave included:
