OL,3,C'A community win': Plans for water
OL,4,Cpark resort in derelict quarry blocked
OL,6,FThose for the development cited that
OL,7,Fit would would have been increased
OL,8,Ftourism, boosting the local economy
OL,9,Fwith 561 jobs.
OL,11,FBut there were objections from more
OL,12,Fthan 700 local residents.
OL,14,FThey argued the main issues were the
OL,15,Feffect on the local environment, on
OL,16,Fnature and the lack of infrastructure
OL,17,Fin terms of roads and access.
OL,19,FHeritage England also objected, saying
OL,20,Fit would potentially harm the world
OL,21,Fheritage site Derwent Valley Mills.
