OL,3,C'A community win': Plans for water
OL,4,Cpark resort in derelict quarry blocked
OL,6,F"The group is thrilled, it's a victory
OL,7,Ffor the community, with 600 members in
OL,8,Four Facebook group, many more in the
OL,9,Fcommunity all on the same page and
OL,10,Fshows what happens when the community
OL,11,Fcomes together with one voice.
OL,13,F"It'll be nice to see the quarry
OL,14,Fbecome more nature habitat lodges".
