OL,3,C'A community win': Plans for water
OL,4,Cpark resort in derelict quarry blocked
OL,6,FIn a statement Derbyshire County
OL,7,FCouncil said:
OL,9,F"Derbyshire County Council's planning
OL,10,Fcommittee considers all planning
OL,11,Fapplications on their merits and is
OL,12,Fimpartial.
OL,14,F"All decisions by the Regulatory
OL,15,FPlanning Committee are made with
OL,16,Fregard to local and national
OL,17,Fdevelopment plans and frameworks and
OL,18,Fare based on proven factual
OL,19,Finformation, information presented to
OL,20,Fthe committee and other material
OL,21,Fconsiderations.
