OL,3,C'A community win': Plans for water
OL,4,Cpark resort in derelict quarry blocked
OL,6,F"For this particular development, all
OL,7,Faspects of the proposal were
OL,8,Fconsidered at the meeting and the
OL,9,Fearlier site visit, and the Committee
OL,10,Fconcluded that the application should
OL,11,Fbe refused for several reasons.
OL,13,F"The applicant has failed to provide a
OL,14,Fsufficiently reliable assessment as to
OL,15,Fthe environmental effects from the
OL,16,Fdevelopment and the development is
OL,17,Fconsidered to conflict with both Local
OL,18,Fdevelopment plan Policy and national
OL,19,Fguidance.
