OL,3,C'A community win': Plans for water
OL,4,Cpark resort in derelict quarry blocked
OL,6,F"Due to a lack of information provided
OL,7,Fto support the proposals, it has not
OL,8,Fbeen demonstrated that the development
OL,9,Fwould not result in significant harm
OL,10,Fcaused to road safety, heritage and
OL,11,Fprotected species and habitats."
OL,13,FThe developers may come back with
OL,14,Faltered plans but the campaigners say
OL,15,Fthey're ready to object again if they
OL,16,Ffeel it isn't right for the area.
